---
id: "JRN_PluginDiscovery"
title: Core Plugin Discovery
description: How the Platform Operator verifies the automatic discovery and loading of community or local plugins.
trigger: System startup or explicit plugin scan.
outcome: Available plugins are registered and ready for execution.
requirements:
  - REQ_Extensibility
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant PER_Operator as Operator
    participant COMP_Engine as Build Engine
    participant COMP_PluginManager as Plugin Manager
    participant FS as File System
    
    PER_Operator->>COMP_Engine: foundryspec build
    COMP_Engine->>COMP_PluginManager: discoverPlugins()
    COMP_PluginManager->>FS: readdir(node_modules)
    FS-->>COMP_PluginManager: [foundryspec-plugin-x, ...]
    COMP_PluginManager-->>COMP_Engine: [PluginX registered]
    COMP_Engine-->>PER_Operator: Build Success (with Plugins)
